{"tid":2092722,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟教你即使移咗民，點樣繼續幫到香港手","createTime":"2020-07-03T11:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T03:24:49.000Z","uid":67553,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"813529c290474972f111840d49da882886dfcbe9","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"我哋成日睇猶太人、波蘭人經歷眾多苦難，但係佢哋究竟點解過咗幾代都仲記得自己本身嘅身份？就係<strong>文化</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋唔知香港人未來會面對啲咩，但係如果選擇去其他地方生活又可以做啲咩？就係盡快搵身邊嘅朋友成立<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港會</span></strong>、長遠要建立<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港國際學校</span></strong>，等全世界都知咩叫香港人──<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>熱愛民主自由、溫文有禮、有智慧、勇敢嘅人</strong></span>。只有咁樣，我哋香港人嘅文化習俗先可以得以保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果真的去到外國，首先梗係要盡快融入人哋社會，學人哋嘅語言、文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n之後當然要同身邊嘅朋友多啲聚會啦！去大家屋企煮下家鄉餸菜，新年、中秋、冬至、<strong>聖誕、復活節</strong>呢啲喺香港會做嘅事，全部都要繼續做！再慢慢做大個餅，認識同一個國家/城市嘅其他香港人，我哋生咗下一代亦都要等佢哋加入呢個圈子。<br />\n<br />\n一步一步做落去，我相信一定可以保留到我哋香港嘅文化同歷史！就算之後再有手足想過嚟，即刻就知可以搵咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9c9156fb9b6769beaa19f3a13ac4a08c7c8e28","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d747698288d40cb9f73ff385ca91ed6022ea1631","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150d8bc66f61b7b169d7b17b454d62dd40d4615d","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17163fc87a55fbc6c81ebfeb70b0e98e77bde0d","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee797d369f19e2552d82f2ef4aaccd1ee6e851a","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b664b805bed4d312c9fff2ddb484fca14d2968b6","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854443f430554b6868f74cb5d9202bec8d364f1c","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1224d5fdf1e369f01606c6dec0a36d9e0353e8","tid":2092722,"uid":218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68326f29b32f973781821fb111e3f8f476bfcede","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4a734bc34eeeedd62a287cea16281f3f7b728a","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a813087b070856dcb313f6a07ee205f1327c3b","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dd14b5f1a1dcbdc16e41702854c73be91a897c","tid":2092722,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T11:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\